A 363 Sq. In. cooking surface gives you plenty of space to cook up your favorite, mouthwatering meals.

properties.full_description: The Weber 18 in. Smokey Mountain Cooker smoker features a generous 481 sq. In. of cooking space across two plated-steel grill grates, enough room to smoke several slabs of ribs and a whole roast concurrently. This charcoal smoker has a built-in lid thermometer with a smoke-zone sweet-spot identifier between 200 and 275°F that makes it easy to monitor heat and regulate accordingly with air dampers and briquette adjustments. To keep foods moist and flavorful, a porcelain-enameled water pan is included for high-humidity slow-cooks that produce juicy, tender, professional-grade results every time.

properties.full_description: The Regal Pellet 500 grill is a powerful and innovative pellet grill that uses a Wifi and Bluetooth® enabled digital controller to provide enhanced temperature control allowing you to do anything with this grill including low-and-slow smoking at 225°F, roasting at 350°F, or even high-heat searing 600°F.. This pellet grill comes fully equipped with a powerful auger, 22-lb capacity pellet hopper, removable grease management system, unique ash management system, deluxe rotisserie kit, 2 electronic meat probes, base storage and side shelf, and heavy duty and reversible cast iron cooking grids. Total cooking space on this grill is 865 sq. in. including a porcelain coated warming rack.
